snippet.title: Best VGM 2426 - Xenoblade Chronicles : Definitive Edition - Bionis' Shoulder
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Switch
Xenoblade Chronicles: Definitive Edition (2020
Bionis' Shoulder
Manami Kiyota & ACE+
